Package freemarker.template

Class Template.WrongEncodingException

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Throwable
java.lang.Exception
java.io.IOException
freemarker.core.ParseException
freemarker.template.Template.WrongEncodingException
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Enclosing class:
Template
public static class Template.WrongEncodingException extends ParseException
Thrown by the Template constructors that specify a non-null encoding whoch doesn't match the encoding specified in the #ftl header of the template.
